trans-unit.target:
Besides Super Magical Chests, chests are not determined by chance, they are determined by a cycle.
The cycle does not advance if you have no empty chest slots. You must have a chest slot open to get the next chest and move forward in the cycle.
There are 180 Silver Chests, 52 Golden Chests, 4 Magical Chests and 4 Giant Chests in the 240 chests cycle.
Super Magical Chests are the only chests given by chance, which is 0.2%. And it will replace the one in the cycle.

trans-unit.target:
You can enter up to 10 of your previous chests.
Magical Chests and Giant Chests are called Rare Chests here.
In the Picker of 2 Previous Rare Chests, right one is your previous Rare Chest, left one is the Rare Chests before your previous Rare Chest.
Base on your input, if your input is valid, the possible coming chests will show up.
Each row of possible coming chests means one possibility.

trans-unit.target:
除了超級神奇寶箱，其它寶箱掉落不是隨機的，它們是由你在寶箱循環的位置決定的。
如果你4個寶箱空位槽滿了，你的寶箱循環不會進位，即使你贏的了一場對戰。
目前寶箱循環表裡總共有180個白銀寶箱，52個黃金寶箱，4個神奇寶箱，4個巨型寶箱總共240個寶箱組成。
超級神奇寶箱是唯一一個由運氣決定的，它的掉落機率是0.2%，同時它會取代你原本要從寶箱循環裡得到的寶箱。

trans-unit.id:

trans-unit.target:
你可以輸入最多10個你最近得到的寶箱。
神奇寶箱和巨型寶箱在這裡統一歸位稀有寶箱。
在“前兩個稀有寶箱”選擇器裡，右邊寶箱代表你的前一個稀有寶箱，左邊寶箱代表前一個的前一個稀有寶箱。
根據你輸入的信息，如果輸入的信息有效，“你接下來的5個寶箱會是”會顯示你可能的結果，每一行代表一個可能的結果。
